# Hunyuan-OCR weight manifest — Tencent's official ModelScope release
# (Tencent-Hunyuan/HunyuanOCR). Single source of truth: the runtime staging
# path (model_stager.rs, via include_str!) and CI (.github/workflows/ci-gpu.yaml,
# via sha256sum --check) both read this file. Update the model → edit here only.
#
# The four safetensors shards are sha256-identical to the (now Hub-unavailable)
# tencent/HunyuanOCR weights. Only the files the engine and processor read are
# listed; model.safetensors.index.json is omitted because the loader discovers
# the shards by directory scan, not through the index.
